data.description: Awesomely updated ranch home over a full basement in a sought-after Gainesville city location! Enjoy TWO kitchens, beautifully refinished hardwood floors upstairs, fresh interior paint, new gutters, custom countertops, custom lighting, and many more recent updates. The main level features a modern kitchen (all electric) with dining area, living space, a newly expanded BR, and an ensuite. Downstairs holds a large multi-use room, BR, additional kitchen (propane), full bath with tub, and access to the fenced backyard. Easily entertain from the two decks or lovely sunroom. Easily rent the bottom unit - it has its own entrance! Situated in a lakefront neighborhood just minutes from all of Gainesville's restaurants, shopping, and entertainment.
